Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 长老不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 杀过来了
